to help visually align and relate names with values.
The width of all "cards" will be equal (probably tighter than
shown here). Overflow from long notes or extremely long
names will be clipped and indicated with "...". Hovering will
show the full text. Extremely large values will be abbreviated
with unit values ($10k, $1.6m). This unit values will be
